1
00:00:01,501 --> 00:00:03,570
I'm so exhausted.

2
00:00:04,904 --> 00:00:07,607
Maybe I should just quit.

3
00:00:08,608 --> 00:00:09,608
Quit?

4
00:00:09,876 --> 00:00:11,110
Your dad was so worried about you

5
00:00:11,111 --> 00:00:13,112
that he had me come back
from Japan to manage you.

6
00:00:13,113 --> 00:00:14,593
And now you're telling me to go back?

7
00:00:15,982 --> 00:00:17,302
I mean, I guess that's an option.

8
00:00:18,518 --> 00:00:20,754
You are seriously wasting my time.

9
00:00:21,688 --> 00:00:23,489
Look, I'm not having it.

10
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:24,990
You're the one who chose this career,

11
00:00:24,991 --> 00:00:26,311
so don't you dare bail on me now.

12
00:00:27,427 --> 00:00:29,528
But what happens when I'm older

13
00:00:29,529 --> 00:00:31,264
and I can't sing or dance anymore?

14
00:00:32,032 --> 00:00:33,599
Look, AKA...

15
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,768
Who was the one who promised me

16
00:00:35,769 --> 00:00:37,203
they'd prove everyone wrong?

17
00:00:37,737 --> 00:00:39,805
From the bottom to the big stage?

18
00:00:39,830 --> 00:00:42,232
It's been days and
there's no word on the ad.

19
00:00:42,942 --> 00:00:44,611
Hei Yan must have found someone else.

20
00:00:55,822 --> 00:00:57,589
Hey, you're buying me dinner.

21
00:00:57,590 --> 00:00:59,726
It's official. "Black &amp; White" is a go.

22
00:01:05,498 --> 00:01:07,133
It's me, you dummy.

23
00:01:08,334 --> 00:01:09,402
I'm the one!

24
00:01:10,937 --> 00:01:11,937
I actually got it!

25
00:01:12,872 --> 00:01:14,339
Since you're part of a duo now,

26
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:16,009
you better nail your public persona.

27
00:01:16,352 --> 00:01:18,511
I want you to win over all his fans
and make them yours.
